        {
            "title": "滬指開市跌7點 深成指跌32點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段偏軟，上證綜指以4125點開市，跌7點或0.18%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報14283點，亦跌32點或0.23%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌1點或0.04%，開報4705點；創業板指數開市報3316點，跌3點或0.09%。</p>\n</div>",
