            "title": "港股開市︱初段造好 恒指升97點報26863點 安踏高開1.51%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股開市初段向上，恒生指數開市報26863點，升97點或0.36%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生科技指數開報5734點，升8點或0.16%；國企指數以9173點開市，升25點或0.28%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股12.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">安踏(02020)擬斥相等於約123億港元收購PUMA近30%股權，該股今早開報77.5元，升1.51%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">紫金黃金(02259)則擬全面收購多倫多上市的聯合黃金，對價相等於280億元人民幣；該股今早開報215元，升2.97%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"安踏官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02020-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"安踏官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/07/02020-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">安踏官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">翰森製藥(03692)擬發46.8億元零息換股債，該股今早逆市跌1.04%，開報39.82元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">方舟健客(06086)折讓近12%配股，該股今早應聲回吐10.61%，以3.37元開市。</p>\n</div>",
